  nyxt
  Nyxt is a keyboard-driven web browser for power users.
  More information: https://nyxt.atlas.engineer.

### emacs-with-nyxt
https://github.com/ag91/emacs-with-nyxt
This is some little hack to make Emacs command Nyxt. In particular this provides a function to browse URLs via Nyxt run via Slime.

#### Articles
- https://nyxt.atlas.engineer/article/emacs-conf.org

### tldr
âžœ  ~ tldr nyxt
  - List all profiles:
    nyxt --list-data-profiles
  - Set the init.lisp file path:
    nyxt --init path/to/file
  - Change the path to the auto-config file:
    nyxt --auto-config path/to/file
  - Print system information:
    nyxt --system-information
